<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3872.1.4>
    dc:creator "Rightmyer, Molly G.; Kono, Yoshiaki; Kohn, Joshua R.; Hung, Keng-Lou James" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "A new species of Triepeolus (Hymenoptera: Apidae), with comments on T. utahensis (Cockerell) and T. melanarius Rightmyer" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230947>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230949> .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230947>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 3. Triepeolus matildae, sp. nov. 1. Dorsal habitus of holotype. 2. Dorsal habitus of male paratype. 3. Pseudopygidial area of holotype. 4. Triepeolus utahensis, pseudopygidial area, female from San Diego." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230947/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.230949>
    dc:description "FIGURES 5 – 6. Triepeolus matildae, sp. nov., male paratype. 5. Ventral metasoma. 6. Pygidial plate. Figures 7 – 8. Triepeolus utahensis, male, from San Diego. 7. Ventral metasoma. 8. Pygidial plate. Figures 9 – 10. Triepeolus melanarius, male, from San Diego. 9. Ventral metasoma. 10. Pygidial plate." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/230949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

